            <thetext>testrunner2&#39;s config should use macros to set the testrunner2.view and testrunner2.testOrigin variants to make switching variant settings easier.

testrunner2.view should be changed so it expects the full name of a view class. This class should be added to the testrunner GUI&#39;s include list and the runner application should instantiate it using qx.Class.getByName. This way, any view class could be used simply by setting a (command-line) macro.</thetext>
